title: LF players for a ranked team
body:
Hey guys and girls,
Currently looking for people to play  ranked 5s with for the rewards, it will basically be a fresh team, currently looking for Top, Jungle and support. I'm currently Silver V and dont mind what rank, Will be aiming to play at regular times such as weekdays in the afternoon and on weekends.
If you're interested add me in game: A1 Marky
